%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as User (Frontend)
    participant API as Spring Boot REST API
    participant Mem as Memory Layer
    participant Jira as Jira Adapter
    participant KB as Vector DB / Knowledge Base
    participant Risk as Risk Agent
    participant Cost as Cost Agent
    participant Sched as Scheduling Agent
    participant Bedrock as Amazon Bedrock (LLM)

    User->>API: Submit project data 
    API->>Mem: Store project context
    API->>Jira: Fetch JIRA issues
    Jira-->>API: Return JIRA issues
    API->>KB: Query embeddings for similar tasks
    KB-->>API: Return knowledge base results

    par Parallel Agent Execution
        API->>Risk: Send tasks + JIRA + KB context
        Risk->>Bedrock: Prompt for risk analysis
        Bedrock-->>Risk: Risk results
        Risk-->>API: Return risks

        API->>Cost: Send tasks + KB context
        Cost->>Bedrock: Prompt for cost optimization
        Bedrock-->>Cost: Cost results
        Cost-->>API: Return cost suggestions

        API->>Sched: Send tasks + JIRA context
        Sched->>Bedrock: Prompt for scheduling
        Bedrock-->>Sched: Schedule results
        Sched-->>API: Return schedule
    end

    API->>API: Aggregate agent outputs
    API-->>User: Unified AI recommendations (JSON)
